xt4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1021127, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 1, "EnglishDescription": "A Person came to Hazrat Rasool’e Khuda (s) and said: I’m very much in debt and there is no way to pay off the debt, so please suggest a solution to this problem. Hazrat (s) ordered him to recite this dua <Fa-lillaa-hil Hamdo Rabis Samawaate> as much as possible, inshallah very soon your problem will be solved. It is in narration that the same man again came to Hazrat (s) and said: my all the debt is paid still I’m in poverty. Hazrat (s) order him to recite the same dua frequently.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Ek shakhs ne Hazrat Rasool’e Khuda (s) ki khidmat mein arz kiya keh mai bohot ziyadah maqrooz (qarz-daar) hu aur qarz ki adaayegi ka koi zariya bhi nahin hai, meri mushkil ka koi hal bayaan farma dijiye. Aan Hazrat (s) ne us ko hukm diya keh is dua <Fa-lillaa-hil Hamdo Rabis Samawaate> ko bohot ziyadah vird kiya karo inshallah ul-azeez bohot jald tumhaari mushkil hal ho jaayegi. Riwaayat mein hai keh wohi shakhs kuchh dino baad dobaara Hazrat Rasool’e Khuda (s) ki khidmat mein haazir huwa aur arz kiya keh mera saara qarz adaa ho chuka hai lekin abhi bhi tang-dast hu. Aap (s) ne usey phir usi dua ke vird ka hukm diya.", "UrduDescription": "ایک شخص نے حضرت رسول اکرمؐ کی خدمت اقدس میں عرض کیا کہ بہت زیادہ مقروض ہوں اور قرض کی ادائیگی کا کوئی ذریعہ بھی نہیں ہے میری مشکل کا کوئی حل بیان فرمادیجئے۔ آنحضرتؐ نے اس کو حکم دیا کہ اس دعا <فَلِلّٰہِ الْحَمْدُ رَبِّ السَّمَوَاتِ> کا بہت زیادہ ورد کیا کرو، انشاء اللہ العزیز بہت جلد تمہاری مشکل حل ہوجائے گی۔ روات میں ہے کہ وہی شخص کچھ دنوں بعد دوبارہ حاضر خدمت ہوا اور عرض کیا کہ میرا سارا قرض ادا ہوچکا ہے لیکن ابھی بھی تنگ دست ہوں، آپؐ نے اسے پھر اسی دعا کے ورد کا حکم دیا۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": 